  "instructions": [
    "heat the coconut oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "add the grass rice blend and stir for 2 minutes.",
    "add the vegetable broth and stir to combine.",
    "bring to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and cover with a tight-fitting lid.",
    "simmer for 20 minutes or until the liquid has been absorbed and the rice is tender.",
